TITLE: Generating Basic Form with JSON Schema in Amis
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to generate a basic form using the `json-schema` component in Amis. It defines a form with an API endpoint for saving data and includes a `json-schema` component that renders form fields based on the provided JSON Schema. The schema defines properties for 'id' (number), 'name' (string), and 'description' (string).
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/json-schema.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    debug: true,
    "body": [
        {
            "type": "json-schema",
            "name": "value",
            "label": "字段值",
            "schema": {
              type: 'object',
              properties: {
                id: {
                  type: 'number',
                  title: 'ID'
                },
                name: {
                  type: 'string',
                  title: '名称'
                },
                description: {
                  type: 'string',
                  title: '描述'
                }
              }
            }
        }
    ]
}
```

