TITLE: Form Schema API Response Example (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This shows the expected JSON response from the `schemaApi` when rendering form elements dynamically.  It should return a container object with a 'body' property containing form items, and optionally, a 'data' property that specifies the initial data for the form.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/service.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "status": 0,
  "msg": "",
  "data": {
    "type": "container",
    "body": [
      {
        "type": "input-text",
        "name": "text",
        "label": "文本输入"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "status": 0,
  "msg": "",
  "data": {
    "data": {
      "a": "b" // 这样返回的选项会选中第二个选项B
    },
    "body": [
      {
        "type": "select",
        "name": "a",
        "label": "选项",
        "options": [
          {"label": "A", "value": "a"},
          {"label": "B", "value": "b"}
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

