TITLE: Configuring CRUD for Nested Data - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This JSON configuration illustrates how to display nested data within a CRUD component. The presence of a 'children' field in the data automatically triggers the display as a tree structure with expand/collapse functionality.  It defines the API and columns to display.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/crud.md#_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "crud",
    "name": "crud",
    "syncLocation": false,
    "api": "/api/mock2/crud/table2",
    "columns": [
        {
            "name": "id",
            "label": "ID"
        },
        {
            "name": "engine",
            "label": "Rendering engine"
        },
        {
            "name": "browser",
            "label": "Browser"
        }
    ]
}
```

