TITLE: Table2 Custom Row Selection Menu
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to customize the row selection menu in the Table2 component using the `selections` property within `rowSelection`.  This example showcases built-in options like 'all', 'invert', 'none', 'odd', and 'even'. Data is from a service.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/table2.md#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "service",
  "api": "/api/sample?perPage=5",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "table2",
      "source": "$rows",
      "rowSelection": {
        "type": "checkbox",
        "keyField": "id",
        "selections": [
          {
            "key": "all",
            "text": "全选所有"
          },
          {
            "key": "invert",
            "text": "反选当页"
          },
          {
            "key": "none",
            "text": "清空所有"
          },
          {
            "key": "odd",
            "text": "选择奇数行"
          },
          {
            "key": "even",
            "text": "选择偶数行"
          }
        ]
      },
      "columns": [
        {
          "title": "Engine",
          "name": "engine"
        },
        {
          "title": "Version",
          "name": "version"
        },
        {
          "title": "Browser",
          "name": "browser"
        },
        {
          "title": "Operation",
          "name": "operation",
          "type": "button",
          "label": "删除",
          "size": "sm"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

