TITLE: Configuring Table Quick Edit with Batch Saving
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to enable quick editing in an AMIS table and configure it for batch saving. It sets `quickEdit` to true for a column and defines the `quickSaveApi` for bulk updates. It also includes actions for reloading the table after a quick save or order change.
