TITLE: Custom Field with Multiple Component Rendering
DESCRIPTION: This example extends the custom field configuration to support rendering multiple components based on the selected operator.  The `values` property within an operator allows specifying multiple components (e.g., input-text) to be rendered in the UI. Each component's configuration is nested under the `values` array with `type` and `name` properties defined.
