TITLE: CRUD Add Button Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This snippet configures a button to open a dialog for adding new data.  It includes a button that triggers a dialog containing a form. The form's API defines how the data is submitted, and the CRUD component is configured to display the data. After successful form submission, the CRUD table automatically refreshes.  The `reload: "none"` option would prevent the automatic refresh.
