TITLE: Configuring Initial Row Selection in Amis CRUD
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to configure initial row selection in an Amis CRUD component using the 'fetchInited' event and 'select' action. The 'fetchInited' event is triggered when the data is initially fetched.  An AJAX request retrieves a list of selected IDs. These IDs are then used to programmatically select the corresponding rows in the CRUD component based on a condition that checks if the row's 'id' is included in the retrieved 'selected' array. The 'setEventData' action stores the selected IDs from the API response into the event data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/crud.md#_snippet_98

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "page",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "crud",
      "api": "/api/mock2/sample",
      "id": "crud_reload1",
      "syncLocation": false,
      "onEvent": {
        "fetchInited": {
          "actions": [
            {
              "actionType": "ajax",
              "api": {
                "method": "get",
                "url": "/mock返回可以随便写",
                "mockResponse": {
                  "staus": 200,
                  "data": {
                    "status": 0,
                    "data": {
                      "selected": [1, 2, 3]
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "actionType": "setEventData",
              "args": {
                "key": "selected",
                "value": "${responseResult.responseData.selected}"
              }
            },
            {
              "actionType": "select",
              "componentId": "crud_reload1",
              "args": {
                "condition": "${ARRAYINCLUDES(selected, id)}"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "bulkActions": [
        {
          "label": "批量操作",
          "type": "button",
          "onEvent": {
            "click": {
              "actions": [
                {
                  "actionType": "toast",
                  "args": {
                    "msg": "${ids}"
                  }
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ],
      "columns": [
        {
          "name": "id",
          "label": "ID"
        },
        {
          "name": "engine",
          "label": "Rendering engine"
        },
        {
          "name": "browser",
          "label": "Browser"
        },
        {
          "name": "platform",
          "label": "Platform(s)"
        },
        {
          "name": "version",
          "label": "Engine version"
        },
        {
          "name": "grade",
          "label": "CSS grade"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

