TITLE: Enabling CSV Export - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This configuration enables CSV export functionality in the CRUD component. Including "export-csv" in the `headerToolbar` or `footerToolbar` array adds a button that allows users to download the currently displayed data as a CSV file.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/crud.md#_snippet_59

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "crud",
    "syncLocation": false,
    "api": "/api/mock2/sample",
    "headerToolbar": ["export-csv"],
    "columns": [
        {
            "name": "id",
            "label": "ID"
        },
        {
            "name": "engine",
            "label": "Rendering engine"
        },
        {
            "name": "browser",
            "label": "Browser"
        },
        {
            "name": "platform",
            "label": "Platform(s)"
        },
        {
            "name": "version",
            "label": "Engine version"
        },
        {
            "name": "grade",
            "label": "CSS grade",
            "type": "mapping",
            "map": {
                "*": "<span class=\"label label-info\">${grade}</span>"
            }
        }
    ]
}
```

