TITLE: Setting Values in Input-Table Component
DESCRIPTION: This configuration demonstrates the usage of the 'setValue' action to update data within an Input-Table component.  A button triggers the action.  The 'componentId' links the button to the Input-Table. The 'args' property contains the 'value' which represents the new data to replace the existing table content. In this example, it replaces all data in the table with new values.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-table.md#_snippet_40

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "button",
      "label": "更新列表记录",
      "onEvent": {
        "click": {
          "actions": [
            {
              "componentId": "setValue-input-table",
              "groupType": "component",
              "actionType": "setValue",
              "args": {
                "value": [
                  {
                    "a": "a-setValue1",
                    "b": "b-setValue1"
                  },
                  {
                    "a": "a-setValue2",
                    "b": "b-setValue2"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "input-table",
      "label": "表格表单",
      "id": "setValue-input-table",
      "name": "table",
      "columns": [
        {
          "name": "a",
          "label": "A"
        },
        {
          "name": "b",
          "label": "B"
        }
      ],
      "addable": true,
      "footerAddBtn": {
        "label": "新增",
        "icon": "fa fa-plus",
        "hidden": true
      },
      "strictMode": true,
      "minLength": 0,
      "needConfirm": false,
      "showTableAddBtn": false
    }
  ],
  "data": {
    "table": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "a": "a1",
        "b": "b1"
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "a": "a2",
        "b": "b2"
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "a": "a3",
        "b": "b3"
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "a": "a4",
        "b": "b4"
      },
      {
        "id": 5,
        "a": "a5",
        "b": "b5"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

