TITLE: Opening a Drawer (Modal) - AMIS JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure a button to open a modal drawer using the `actionType: 'drawer'` property in AMIS. It defines the drawer's title, body content (a simple text template), and event handlers for 'confirm' and 'cancel' actions, which trigger toast messages.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/event-action.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  type: 'page',
  body: [
    {
      type: 'button',
      id: 'b_004',
      level: 'primary',
      label: '打开抽屉（模态）',
      onEvent: {
        click: {
          actions: [
            {
              actionType: 'drawer',
              drawer: {
                type: 'drawer',
                title: '模态抽屉',
                body: [
                  {
                    type: 'tpl',
                    tpl: '<p>对，你打开了模态抽屉</p>',
                    inline: false
                  }
                ],
                onEvent: {
                  confirm: {
                    actions: [
                      {
                        actionType: 'toast',
                        args: {
                          msg: 'confirm'
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  cancel: {
                    actions: [
                      {
                        actionType: 'toast',
                        args: {
                          msg: 'cancel'
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

