TITLE: Opening a Confirmation Dialog - AMIS JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to open a confirmation dialog using `actionType: 'confirmDialog'`. It includes a title and message that are dynamically populated from the page's data.  The `env.confirm` function needs to be implemented in the environment. A toast message is displayed after a successful confirmation.
