TITLE: IsEquals Filter Example
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to use the `isEquals` filter to compare string literals. It checks if `text1` and `text2` are strictly equal to 'Hello' and displays '等于' or '不等于' accordingly.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/data-mapping.md#_snippet_76

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "page",
  "data": {
    "text1": "Hello",
    "text2": "hello"
  },
  "body": [
    {
        "type": "tpl",
        "tpl": "${text1|isEquals:'Hello':'等于':'不等于'}" // 输出: 等于
    },
    {
        "type": "divider"
    },
    {
        "type": "tpl",
        "tpl": "${text2|isEquals:'Hello':'等于':'不等于'}" // 输出: 等于
    }
  ]
}
```

