TITLE: Basic List Usage with Service API in Amis (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the basic implementation of an Amis List component integrated with a Service component to fetch and display data. The Service component calls an API endpoint to retrieve data, and the List component renders the data using the '$rows' source and a specified listItem configuration.  It shows how to display data in a tabular format with "Engine" and "Version" columns and includes a "view details" button that opens a dialog box.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/list.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "service",
  "api": "/api/mock2/sample?perPage=5",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "list",
      "source": "$rows",
      "listItem": {
        "body": [
          {
            "type": "hbox",
            "columns": [
              {
                "label": "Engine",
                "name": "engine"
              },

              {
                "name": "version",
                "label": "Version"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "button",
            "level": "link",
            "label": "查看详情",
            "actionType": "dialog",
            "dialog": {
              "title": "查看详情",
              "body": {
                "type": "form",
                "body": [
                  {
                    "label": "Engine",
                    "name": "engine",
                    "type": "static"
                  },
                  {
                    "name": "version",
                    "label": "Version",
                    "type": "static"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

