TITLE: InputExcel with InputTable Integration
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates integrating InputExcel with the InputTable component. When an Excel file is uploaded via InputExcel, the resulting data is displayed in an editable InputTable. The `name` property must be consistent between components, and the column names in InputTable must match the Excel column headers.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-excel.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    "body": [
        {
          "type": "input-excel",
          "name": "excel",
          "label": "上传 Excel",
          "placeholder": "请拖拽Excel文件到当前区域"
        },
        {
          "type": "input-table",
          "name": "excel",
          "visibleOn": "data.excel",
          "columns": [
            {
              "name": "名称",
              "label": "名称",
              "type": "input-text"
            },
            {
              "name": "网址",
              "label": "网址",
              "type": "input-text"
            }
          ]
        }
    ]
}
```

