TITLE: Enabling Drag and Drop Sorting in Table2 - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This JSON snippet configures an Amis Table2 component to enable drag-and-drop sorting. By setting `draggable` to `true`, users can manually reorder rows in the table.  The `keyField` specifies the unique identifier for each row, ensuring that the sorting is correctly applied to the underlying data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/table2.md#_snippet_22

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "service",
  "api": "/api/sample?perPage=5",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "table2",
      "source": "$rows",
      "draggable": true,
      "keyField": "id",
      "columns": [
        {
          "title": "ID",
          "name": "id"
        },
        {
          "title": "Grade",
          "name": "grade"
        },
        {
          "title": "Browser",
          "name": "browser"
        },
        {
          "title": "Badge",
          "name": "badgeText",
          "children": [
            {
              "title": "Engine",
              "name": "engine"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Platform",
          "name": "platform"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Enabling Column Toggling in Amis Table2
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema configures an Amis Table2 component with column toggling enabled.  Setting `columnsTogglable` to `true` provides a user interface to show/hide columns. It is suitable for tables with many columns. The table fetches data from the "/api/sample?perPage=6" API endpoint.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/table2.md#_snippet_29

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "service",
  "api": "/api/sample?perPage=6",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "table2",
      "source": "$rows",
      "columnsTogglable": true,
      "title": "表格的标题",
      "columns": [
        {
          "title": "Engine",
          "name": "engine",
          "width": 200
        },
        {
          "title": "Version",
          "name": "version",
          "width": 200
        },
        {
          "title": "Browser",
          "name": "browser",
          "width": 200,
          "children": [
            {
              "title": "Grade",
              "name": "grade",
              "width": 200
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Badge",
          "name": "badgeText"
        },
        {
          "title": "Platform",
          "name": "platform"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

