TITLE: Implementing Immediate Saving with API Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure immediate saving within AMIS table quick edit directly through API calls configured with the `saveImmediately` property. Instead of just setting the value to true, an api endpoint is specified, triggering this endpoint on changes. Includes an example with select and switch types.
