TITLE: Form auto-fill with API configuration
DESCRIPTION: This snippet configures form auto-fill using the `autoFill.api` property. When the form loads or the input field receives focus, the API is called, and the returned data is automatically mapped to the corresponding form fields using `fillMapping`. The URL also includes parameters based on the current value of browser and version input field.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/formitem.md#_snippet_43

LANGUAGE: schema
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "input-text",
      "label": "浏览器",
      "name": "browser",
      "autoFill": {
        showSuggestion: false,
        "fillMapping": {
          browser: "${browser}",
          version: "${version}",
          platform: '${platform1}'
        },
        api: {
          url: "/api/mock2/form/autoUpdate?browser=${browser}&version=${version}",
          responseData: {
            browser: "${browser}",
            version: "${version}",
            platform1: "${platform}",
          },
          silent: false
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "input-text",
      "label": "版本",
      "name": "version"
    },
    {
      "type": "input-text",
      "label": "平台",
      "name": "platform"
    },
  ]
}
```

