TITLE: TreeSelect with Remote Search Options
DESCRIPTION: This configuration demonstrates how to enable remote searching in the tree-select component using the 'autoComplete' property. The 'autoComplete' endpoint is used to fetch search results based on the 'term' parameter. The 'source' property fetches the initial data. The form submits data to the /api/mock2/form/saveForm endpoint. Requires amis version 2.7.1 or above.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/treeselect.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "type":"form",
    "api":"/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    "body":[
        {
            "type":"tree-select",
            "name":"tree",
            "label":"Tree",
            "autoComplete":"/api/mock2/tree/search?term=$term",
            "source":"/api/mock2/tree/search"
        }
    ]
}
```

