TITLE: Configuring Input-Text with Blur Event - JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema configures an input-text component within an Amis form. It defines a 'blur' event that triggers a toast notification displaying the input value when the input loses focus.  Requires `showInput` to be true for the event to fire.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-text.md#_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "debug": true,
    "body": [
      {
        "name": "text",
        "type": "input-text",
        "label": "text",
        "onEvent": {
            "blur": {
                "actions": [
                    {
                      "actionType": "toast",
                      "args": {
                          "msg": "${event.data.value|json}"
                      }
                    }
                ]
            }
        }
      }
    ]
  }
```

