TITLE: Copying Values to Combo
DESCRIPTION: This JSON configuration demonstrates how to copy values from a CRUD list into an Amis combo component. It utilizes a dialog containing a CRUD component. Clicking the copy button in the CRUD row fills the combo field with the selected row's data. Key configurations involve setting an ID for the combo, using data mapping for the combo index, and employing the `setValue` action with special syntax `${&}` to retrieve the entire data object.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/combo.md#_snippet_22

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "mode": "horizontal",
  "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "combo",
      "name": "combo",
      "id": "thecombo",
      "multiple": true,
      "value": [
        {
          "engine": ""
        }
      ],
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "engine",
          "type": "input-text"
        },
        {
          "label": "Copy",
          "type": "button",
          "actionType": "dialog",
          "size": "md",
          "dialog": {
            "title": "历史记录",
            "actions": [],
            "data": {
              "comboIndex": "${index}"
            },
            "body": [
              {
                "type": "crud",
                "api": "/api/mock2/sample",
                "columns": [
                  {
                    "label": "Engine",
                    "name": "engine"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "operation",
                    "label": "操作",
                    "buttons": [
                      {
                        "label": "复制",
                        "type": "button",
                        "close": true,
                        "onEvent": {
                          "click": {
                            "actions": [
                              {
                                "componentId": "thecombo",
                                "actionType": "setValue",
                                "args": {
                                  "index": "${comboIndex}",
                                  "value": "${&}"
                                }
                              }
                            ]
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

