TITLE: Form Item Validation in InputTable - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This example showcases how to add validation rules to form items within the InputTable component's columns. This ensures that the data entered by the user meets specific criteria, such as requiring numeric input or selecting an option from a list.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-table.md#_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
