TITLE: Service for Interface Linkage (Schema)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates using the Service component to achieve interface linkage. The Service's API is dependent on the value of another component (in this case, a select). When the select value changes, the Service's API is re-triggered.  The API endpoint includes a template string that is dynamically replaced with the selected value.
