TITLE: InputText Add-on Component - Amis
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates adding an add-on component (a button in this case) to the `input-text` component. The `addOn` property defines the button configuration, including its type, icon, and label. When the button is clicked, it can trigger custom actions or behaviors. The form submits to the `/api/mock2/form/saveForm` endpoint.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-text.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    "body": [
        {
            "name": "text",
            "type": "input-text",
            "label": "text",
            "addOn": {
                "type": "button",
                "icon": "https://suda.cdn.bcebos.com/images%2F2021-01%2Fsearch.svg",
                "label": "搜索"
            }
        }
    ]
}
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: CRUD Delete Button Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This JSON snippet configures a delete button within the CRUD component's operation column.  It utilizes an AJAX action type to send a delete request to the specified API endpoint.  A confirmation prompt is displayed before executing the deletion.  After successful deletion, the CRUD table automatically refreshes.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/crud.md#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "crud",
    "api": "/api/mock2/sample?orderBy=id&orderDir=desc",
    "syncLocation": false,
    "columns": [
        {
            "name": "id",
            "label": "ID"
        },
        {
            "name": "engine",
            "label": "Rendering engine"
        },
        {
            "name": "browser",
            "label": "Browser"
        },
        {
            "type": "operation",
            "label": "操作",
            "buttons": [
                {
                    "label": "删除",
                    "type": "button",
                    "actionType": "ajax",
                    "level": "danger",
                    "confirmText": "确认要删除？",
                    "api": "delete:/api/mock2/sample/${id}"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
```

