TITLE: Limiting Date Range with Templates
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates limiting the date range using templates to ensure that the 'start' date is not after the 'end' date, and vice versa.  It uses the values of the 'start' and 'end' fields to dynamically set the `maxDate` and `minDate` properties. The form is configured to send data to the '/api/mock2/form/saveForm' endpoint. Debugging is enabled.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-date.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "debug": true,
    "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    "body": [
        {
            "type": "input-date",
            "name": "start",
            "label": "开始日期",
            "maxDate": "$end"
        },
        {
            "type": "input-date",
            "name": "end",
            "label": "结束日期",
            "minDate": "$start"
        }
    ]
}
```

