TITLE: Table2 with Fixed Header and Row Actions
DESCRIPTION: This snippet showcases how to implement a Table2 component with a fixed header and row actions. The 'scroll' property with 'y: 100' is used to fix the header.  Similar to the previous example, it includes '编辑' (edit) and '删除' (delete) row actions. Data is fetched from '/api/sample?perPage=20'.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/table2.md#_snippet_59

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "service",
  "api": "/api/sample?perPage=20",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "table2",
      "source": "$rows",
      "itemActions": [
        {
          "label": "编辑",
          "type": "button",
          "actionType": "dialog",
          "dialog": {
            "title": "编辑",
            "body": "这是个简单的编辑弹框"
