TITLE: Using Data Provider with Interval and Cleanup in Amis Service
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates using the `dataProvider` property to set up an interval for updating data and returning a cleanup function to clear the interval when the component is destroyed. `setData` is used to update data and `clearInterval` is used for cleanup.
