TITLE: Accessing Context Data in Event Actions (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema demonstrates how to access event data (`${event.data}`) and component data (`${__rendererData}`) within event actions. It includes a form with input fields for 'name' and 'age', where changes trigger toast notifications displaying the input values and the component's data context.
