TITLE: Associated Select Mode - Single Select (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet configures an Amis select component in associated selection mode (`selectMode: "associated"`). It divides the selection into two parts: a left panel and a right panel.  The `leftOptions` define the options in the left panel, and the `options` define the options for the right panel, associated by `ref` values. The `leftMode` is set to "tree".
