DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to add prefixes and suffixes to the `input-text` component. The `prefix` and `suffix` properties can be used to display static text or data-bound values before and after the input field, respectively.  The form submits to the `/api/mock2/form/saveForm` endpoint, using a mock data object to provide the unit.
