TITLE: Big Number Support - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema shows how to enable big number support using the `big` property for an InputNumber component in Amis. When `big` is set to true, the input and output are strings, allowing the input of numbers beyond JavaScript's standard number range.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-number.md#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
