TITLE: InputText Auto-Completion - Amis
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to enable auto-completion for the `input-text` component. The `autoComplete` property specifies the API endpoint to fetch auto-completion suggestions based on the entered text. The `$term` variable in the URL represents the current input value. The form submits to an unspecified endpoint and is in debug mode.
