TITLE: Dynamic Tabs with Source - JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to dynamically generate tabs based on a data source. The `source` property is bound to an array (`arr`) which contains objects with `a` and `b` properties. The `tabs` array uses the `${a}` expression to display the `a` property as the tab title, and renders the `b` property within the tab body using a `tpl` component. The `number` filter formats the `b` value as a number.
