TITLE: Amis setValue Action: Update Specific Rows by Condition
DESCRIPTION: This snippet configures a button that, when clicked, executes the 'setValue' action to update specific rows in the list based on a condition. It targets a component with the ID 'cards_setvalue_item'. The `condition` argument is an Amis expression that determines which rows will be updated. The `value` argument contains the new data for those rows.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/cards.md#_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
        "type": "button",
        "label": "更新version=7的行记录",
        "onEvent": {
          "click": {
            "actions": [
              {
                "actionType": "setValue",
                "componentId": "cards_setvalue_item",
                "args": {
                  "value": {
                    "engine": "amis",
                    "browser": "Chrome",
                    "platform": "Mac Pro",
                    "version": "4",
                    "grade": "Y",
                    "badgeText": "你好！",
                    "id": 1234
                  },
                  "condition": "${version === '7'}"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        }
    },
    {
        "type": "button",
        "label": "更新version=4的行记录",
        "onEvent": {
          "click": {
            "actions": [
              {
                "actionType": "setValue",
                "componentId": "cards_setvalue_item",
                "args": {
                  "value": {
                    "engine": "amis",
                    "browser": "Chrome",
                    "platform": "Mac Pro",
                    "version": "4",
                    "grade": "Y",
                    "badgeText": "你好！",
                    "id": 1234
                  },
                  "condition": {
                      conjunction: 'and',
                      children: [
                        {
                          left: {
                            type: 'field',
                            field: 'version'
                          },
                          op: 'equal',
                          right: "4"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        }
    }
```

