TITLE: Rebuild Action Configuration (AMIS Schema)
DESCRIPTION: This example illustrates how to use the `rebuild` action to dynamically change the schema of a service component. The button group allows the user to choose a `schemaType` (form, tabs, or crud), and the `rebuild` action updates the schema of the service with ID `service-rebuild` based on the selected type. The service uses a `schemaApi` to fetch the schema based on the `schemaType` parameter.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/service.md#_snippet_30

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
[
  {
    "type": "alert",
    "body": "请选择一种构建方式生成组件",
    "level": "info",
    "showIcon": true,
    "className": "mb-3",
    "visibleOn": "this.schemaType == null"
  },
  {
    "type": "button-group",
    "tiled": true,
    "className": "mb-3",
    "buttons": [
      {
        "type": "action",
        "label": "构建form",
        "icon": "fa fa-hammer",
        "onEvent": {
          "click": {
            "actions": [
              {
                "actionType": "rebuild",
                "componentId": "service-rebuild",
                "args": {
                  "schemaType": "form"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "action",
        "label": "构建tabs",
        "icon": "fa fa-hammer",
        "onEvent": {
          "click": {
            "actions": [
              {
                "actionType": "rebuild",
                "componentId": "service-rebuild",
                "args": {
                  "schemaType": "tabs"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "action",
        "label": "构建crud",
        "icon": "fa fa-hammer",
        "onEvent": {
          "click": {
            "actions": [
              {
                "actionType": "rebuild",
                "componentId": "service-rebuild",
                "args": {
                  "schemaType": "crud"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "service",
    "id": "service-rebuild",
    "name": "service-rebuild",
    "schemaApi": {
      "url": "/api/mock2/service/schema?type=${schemaType}",
      "method": "post",
      "sendOn": "this.schemaType != null"
    }
  }
]
```

