TITLE: Simplified GraphQL Query (AMIS >= 1.8.0)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows the simplified GraphQL integration introduced in AMIS version 1.8.0 and later. It uses the `graphql` property to directly specify the GraphQL mutation. The `data` object is automatically treated as variables.  It simplifies configuration compared to older versions.
