TITLE: InputFile AutoFill with Multiple Selections
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows how to use `autoFill` in a multi-select file upload scenario. It uses the `items` variable along with `pick` and `last` functions to extract data from the selected files and populate other form fields. It extracts all URLs to `myUrl` and the last uploaded file url to `lastUrl`. Requires the API response to provide a URL for each file.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-file.md#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: json
