TITLE: Custom Confirmation Dialog - AMIS JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to create a custom confirmation dialog with a form using `actionType: 'confirmDialog'`. The dialog's body is defined with a form that includes input fields and a template.  Clicking "确认" will proceed to the toast message, while clicking "取消" will halt the action chain.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/event-action.md#_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  type: 'page',
  data: {
    title: '操作确认',
    msg: '确认提交吗？'
  },
  body: [
    {
      type: 'button',
      label: '自定义确认对话框（模态）',
      level: 'primary',
      onEvent: {
        click: {
          actions: [
            {
              actionType: 'confirmDialog',
              dialog: {
                type: 'dialog',
                title: '${title}',
                confirmText: '确认',
                cancelText: '取消',
                confirmBtnLevel: 'primary',
                data: {
                  '&': '$$',
                  title: '确认'
                },
                body: [
                  {
                    "type": "form",
                    "initApi": "/api/mock2/form/initData",
                    "title": "编辑用户信息",
                    "body": [
                      {
                        "type": "input-text",
                        "name": "name",
                        "label": "姓名"
                      },
                      {
                        "type": "input-text",
                        "name": "email",
                        "label": "邮箱"
                      },
                      {
                        type: 'tpl',
                        tpl: '${msg}'
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              actionType: 'toast',
              args: {
                msg: '确认ok啦！'
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

