TITLE: Button Click Event with Toast Action
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to configure an action to be performed when the button is clicked.  Specifically it uses the `onEvent` property to register a `click` event, which then executes a toast action, displaying the event type as a message.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/action.md#_snippet_37

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "button",
  "label": "Button",
  "onEvent": {
    "click": {
      "actions": [
        {
          "actionType": "toast",
          "args": {
            "msgType": "info",
            "msg": "${event.context.nativeEvent.type}"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

