TITLE: Server-side validation for Combo fields
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to implement server-side validation for Combo form fields. The example includes a form with two Combo components, `combo1` and `combo2`, and the API response contains error messages mapped to specific fields within the combo instances using path keys such as `combo1[1].a` and `combo2.b`. The API endpoint will be called on form submission.
