TITLE: InputImage with Width Restriction - JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema configures the InputImage component to accept only images with a minimum width of 1000 pixels. The 'limit' property contains a 'minWidth' key set to 1000.  The 'receiver' property specifies the API endpoint for handling the uploaded files, and upon form submission, the uploaded image URL is sent to the '/api/mock2/form/saveForm' endpoint.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-image.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    "body": [
        {
            "type": "input-image",
            "name": "image",
            "label": "限制只能上传宽度大于 1000 的图片",
            "accept": ".jpg",
            "limit": {
