TITLE: Configuring Quick Edit with Immediate Save in Amis CRUD (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This JSON configuration demonstrates how to enable immediate saving of edited form items within an Amis CRUD component using the `quickEdit` property. It sets `saveImmediately` to `true` and specifies the `quickSaveItemApi` endpoint for saving individual items.  It includes configurations for a select and a switch component with inline editing.
