SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/combo.md#_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "debug": true,
  "mode": "horizontal",
  "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
  "body": [
    {
        "type": "combo",
        "name": "combo",
        "label": "拖拽排序",
        "multiple": true,
        "value": [
            {
                "text": "1",
                "select": "a"
            },
            {
                "text": "2",
                "select": "b"
            }
        ],
        "draggable": true,
        "items": [
            {
                "name": "text",
                "type": "input-text"
            },
            {
                "name": "select",
                "type": "select",
                "options": [
                    "a",
                    "b",
                    "c"
                ]
            }
