TITLE: Overriding Data in Amis Dialog with setValue
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to override the existing data in an Amis dialog component with new data using the `setValue` action and the `dataMergeMode: "override"` property. The `setValue` action within the button's `onClick` event updates the `username` field in the dialog with the id `dialog_setvalue2`. Because `dataMergeMode` is set to `override`, only the provided data is retained, effectively deleting any existing fields not included in the provided data, in this case, `password` field.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/dialog.md#_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "button",
    "label": "弹个表单",
    "actionType": "dialog",
    "dialog": {
        "title": "在弹框中的表单",
        "id": "dialog_setvalue2",
        "data": {
          "username": "amis",
          "password": "amis@baidu.com"
        },
        "body": [
          {
            "type": "alert",
            "body": "初始化时，弹窗的数据data为{username: 'amis', password: 'fex'}，表单内或者表单外都可以读取这些数据，当点击【更新弹窗数据】按钮后，弹窗的数据被更新为{username: 'aisuda'}，即password将被删除"
          },
          {
            "type": "input-text",
            "label": "表单外的密码",
            "name": "password"
          },
          {
            "type": "form",
            "debug": true,
            "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm?waitSeconds=2",
            "body": [
                {
                    "type": "input-text",
                    "name": "username",
                    "required": true,
                    "placeholder": "请输入用户名",
                    "label": "用户名"
                },
                {
                    "type": "input-password",
                    "name": "password",
                    "label": "密码",
                    "required": true,
                    "placeholder": "请输入密码"
                }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "button",
            "label": "更新弹窗数据",
            "onEvent": {
              "click": {
                "actions": [
                  {
                    "actionType": "setValue",
                    "componentId": "dialog_setvalue2",
                    "args": {
                      "value": {
                        "username": "aisuda"
                      }
                    },
                    "dataMergeMode": "override"
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          }
        ]
    }
}
```

