TITLE: Set Progress Value - JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema illustrates how to use the `setValue` action with the Amis Progress component.  It defines a page with a progress bar and a button.  Clicking the button triggers the `setValue` action on the progress component, updating its value to 20. The `componentId` specifies the target progress component, and the `value` argument in `args` sets the new progress value.
