TITLE: Configuring 'clear' Action for Amis Combo
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to configure the 'clear' action for an Amis Combo component. A button is configured to trigger the 'clear' action on the combo component with the ID 'clear_type'. When the button is clicked, the combo component's value is cleared.  The combo contains text and select input types, initialized with default values. The action is triggered via the `onEvent` property of the button.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/combo.md#_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "debug": true,
    "body": [
      {
        "type": "combo",
        "name": "type",
        "id": "clear_type",
        "label": "用户",
        "items": [
          {
            "name": "text",
