TITLE: Feedback Dialog with Form Submission - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates a feedback dialog containing a form that submits data and closes all dialogs upon success.  The feedback's body is a form itself, and the confirm action triggers its submission.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/dialog.md#_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "button",
  "label": "弹一个框",
  "actionType": "dialog",
  "dialog": {
    "body": {
        "type": "form",
        "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm?waitSeconds=2",
        "body": [
            {
                "type": "input-text",
                "name": "text",
                "required": true,
                "label": "用户名",
