TITLE: SetValue Action Configuration (AMIS Schema)
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to use the `setValue` action to update the data of a service component. Clicking the button will trigger the action, merging the specified `value` (name and email) into the data of the service with ID `service-setvalue`. This configuration shows how to update a component's data by merging new values with existing ones.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/service.md#_snippet_31

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
[
    {
      "type": "button",
      "label": "更新数据",
      "onEvent": {
        "click": {
          "actions": [
            {
              "actionType": "setValue",
              "componentId": "service-setvalue",
              "args": {
                "value": {
                  "name": "aisuda",
                  "email": "aisuda@baidu.com"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "service",
      "id": "service-setvalue",
      "name": "service-setvalue",
      "data": {
        "name": "amis",
        "email": "amis@baidu.com"
      },
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "tpl",
          "tpl": "名字：${name|default:'-'}，邮箱：${email|default:'-'}"
        }
      ]
    }
]
```

