TITLE: InputDateRange Storing Data in Two Fields
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to configure the InputDateRange component to store the start and end dates in separate fields. By setting 'extraName', the end date will be stored in a field with that name, while the start date is stored in the field specified by 'name'.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-date-range.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "debug": true,
    "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    "body": [
        {
            "type": "input-date-range",
            "name": "begin",
            "extraName": "end",
            "label": "日期范围"
        }
    ]
}
```

