TITLE: Configuring CRUD for Lazy Loading (Nested Data) - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This JSON configuration demonstrates implementing lazy loading for nested data within an AMIS CRUD component.  It configures a 'deferApi' endpoint, which is called only when a node with the 'defer: true' property is expanded. The deferApi returns the details of the node, including its children, enabling on-demand loading of nested data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/crud.md#_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "crud",
    "name": "crud",
    "syncLocation": false,
    "api": "/api/mock2/crud/table6",
    "deferApi": "/api/mock2/crud/table6?parentId=${id}",
    "columns": [
        {
            "name": "id",
            "label": "ID"
        },
        {
            "name": "engine",
            "label": "Rendering engine"
        },
        {
            "name": "browser",
            "label": "Browser"
        }
    ]
}
```

