TITLE: Configuring popOver for Column Content - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure the `popOver` attribute for a column within an amis table. When a user clicks on the column content, a popover will appear displaying additional information. The `popOver` property includes a `body` object that defines the content to be displayed in the popover using a template.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/table.md#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "page",
    "data": {
        "table": [
            {
                "id": 1,
                "text": "The longest word in any of the major English language dictionaries is pneumonoultramicroscopicsilicovolcanoconiosis, a word that refers to a lung disease contracted from the inhalation of very fine silica particles, specifically from a volcano; medically, it is the same as silicosis."
            },
            {
                "id": 2,
                "text": "The longest word in any of the major English language dictionaries is pneumonoultramicroscopicsilicovolcanoconiosis, a word that refers to a lung disease contracted from the inhalation of very fine silica particles, specifically from a volcano; medically, it is the same as silicosis."
            }
        ]
    },
    "body": [
        {
            "type": "crud",
            "source": "${table}",
            "columns": [
                {
                    "name": "id",
                    "label": "ID"
                },
                {
                    "type": "container",
                    "style": {
                        "display": "inline-block"
                    },
                    "body": {
                        "type": "tpl",
                        "name": "text",
                        "label": "long text",
                        "className": "text-ellipsis",
                        "style": {
                            "max-width": "300px"
                        },
                    },
                    "popOver": {
                        "body": {
                            "type": "tpl",
                            "tpl": "${text}"
                        }
                    }
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
```

