TITLE: Configuring Select EditConfirm Event
DESCRIPTION: This JSON configuration defines an editable select component with an onEvent handler for the 'editConfirm' event. When an existing option is edited and confirmed, a toast message displays the edited item's data using the event data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/select.md#_snippet_26

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
  "debug": true,
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "select",
      "name": "tree",
      "label": "Tree",
      "creatable": true,
      "removable": true,
      "editable": true,
      "onEvent": {
        "editConfirm": {
          "actions": [
            {
              "actionType": "toast",
              "args": {
                "msg": "${event.data.item|json}"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "value": "a"
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "value": "b"
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "value": "c"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

