DESCRIPTION: This JSON configuration uses a custom character for the InputRating component stars. The 'char' property is set to '好', replacing the default star character. The component name is 'rating', label is '评分', and the form's API is '/api/mock2/form/saveForm'.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-rating.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: JSON
