TITLE: Configuring Link Button
DESCRIPTION: Configures a button that navigates to another page within the Amis platform. The `actionType` is set to `link`, and the `link` property specifies the relative URL of the target page.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/action.md#_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: JSON
