TITLE: Associated Select Mode - Multiple Select (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet configures an Amis select component in associated selection mode with multiple selections enabled (`multiple: true`). It also uses `leftMode: "tree"` and allows searching using `searchable: true`.  Similar to the single select example, options are dynamically loaded using `deferApi`.
