TITLE: Customizing Placeholders - Amis JSON
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to customize the placeholder text for the key and value input fields in the `input-kv` component using the `keyPlaceholder` and `valuePlaceholder` properties.  Requires Amis library and a backend API endpoint. The `name` property specifies the key in the form data where the key-value pairs will be stored.
