TITLE: InputImage with File Type Restriction - JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema configures the InputImage component to accept only '.jpg' files. The 'accept' property is set to '.jpg', restricting the file selection dialog to show only JPG images.  The 'receiver' property specifies the API endpoint for handling the uploaded files, and upon form submission, the uploaded image URL is sent to the '/api/mock2/form/saveForm' endpoint.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-image.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    "body": [
        {
            "type": "input-image",
            "name": "image",
            "label": "限制只能上传jpg图片",
            "accept": ".jpg",
            "receiver": "/api/upload/file"
        }
    ]
}
```

