TITLE: Polling API for Page Data in Amis
DESCRIPTION: This snippet configures the Amis Page to poll an API endpoint for data at a specified interval. It includes an option to stop polling based on a condition. The `initApi` sets the API, `interval` defines the polling frequency, and `stopAutoRefreshWhen` specifies the condition to stop polling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/page.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "page",
  "initApi": "/api/mock2/page/initData",
  "interval": 3000,
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "tpl",
      "tpl": "当前时间是：${date}"
    }
  ]
}
```

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "page",
  "initApi": "/api/mock2/page/initData",
  "stopAutoRefreshWhen": "this.time % 5", // 当时间戳能被5整除时，停止轮询
  "interval": 3000,
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "tpl",
      "tpl": "当前时间戳是：${date}"
    }
  ]
}
```

