TITLE: Office Viewer Download Action (Schema)
DESCRIPTION: This code implements a download action for an office-viewer component. It configures an "action" button that, when clicked, triggers the "saveAs" action on the "office-viewer-download" component, downloading the linked document. The office-viewer component is set to display: false, so it's only used for the download functionality.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/office-viewer.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
[
  {
    "type": "action",
    "label": "下载文档",
    "onEvent": {
        "click": {
          "actions": [
            {
              "actionType": "saveAs",
              "componentId": "office-viewer-download"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
  },
  {
    "type": "office-viewer",
    "id": "office-viewer-download",
    "display": false,
    "src": "/examples/static/simple.docx"
  }
]
```

