TITLE: IFrame to Amis Communication - onEvent Configuration - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This JSON snippet demonstrates the usage of `onEvent` to configure the Amis IFrame component to listen for messages from the iframe. It handles the 'detail' event with multiple actions: displaying a dialog and updating a component.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/iframe.md#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "iframe",
  "src": "http://www.xxx.com",
  "onEvent": {
    "detail": {
      "actions": [
        // 动作 1，弹窗动作
        {
          "actionType": "dialog",
          "dialog": {
            "title": "弹框",
            "body": "iframe 传给 amis 的 id 是：${iframeId}" // 在弹框中渲染`"iframe 传给 amis 的 id 是：${iframeId}"`这段模板，即111
          }
        },
        // 动作 2，触发指定组件的特性动作
        {
          "actionType": "crud",
          "componentId": "form01",
          "data": {
            "iframeId": "${iframeId}" // 刷新请求参数为`"iframe 传给 amis 的 id 是：${iframeId}"`这段模板，即111
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

