TITLE: Accessing HTTP Response Data in AMIS Actions
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema demonstrates how to access data returned from an HTTP request within subsequent actions in AMIS. A button triggers an AJAX request. Upon successful completion, a dialog is displayed, populated with data extracted from the AJAX response. Data is accessed using `${event.data.responseResult.responseData.id}`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/event-action.md#_snippet_24

LANGUAGE: schema
CODE:
```
{
  type: 'page',
  body: [
    {
      type: 'button',
      label: '发送Ajax请求，并把返回数据传给弹窗',
      level: 'primary',
      onEvent: {
        click: {
          actions: [
            {
              actionType: 'ajax',
              args: {
                api: 'https://3xsw4ap8wah59.cfc-execute.bj.baidubce.com/api/amis-mock/mock2/form/saveForm'
              }
            },
            {
              actionType: 'dialog',
              data: {
                id: '${event.data.responseResult.responseData.id}'
              },
              dialog: {
                type: 'dialog',
                id: 'dialog_005',
                title: '弹框标题1',
                data: {
                  id: '${id}'
                },
                body: [
                  {
                    type: 'form',
                    body: [
                      {
                        type: 'tpl',
                        tpl: '<p>请求返回的数据：id=${id}</p>',
                        inline: false
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

