TITLE: Checkboxes with Custom Option Rendering - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This configuration uses the `menuTpl` property to customize the rendering of the checkboxes options.  It allows for injecting HTML and data binding to render each option with a specific class based on the `klass` property of the option. This enhances visual presentation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/checkboxes.md#_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    "body": [
        {
            "name": "checkboxes",
            "type": "checkboxes",
            "label": "复选框",
            "menuTpl": "<span class='label label-${klass}'>${label}</span>",
            "options": [
                {
                    "label": "OptionA",
                    "value": "a",
                    "klass": "success"
                },
                {
                    "label": "OptionB",
                    "value": "b",
                    "klass": "danger"
                },
                {
                    "label": "OptionC",
                    "value": "c",
                    "klass": "warning"
                },
                {
                    "label": "OptionD",
                    "value": "d",
                    "klass": "info"
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
```

