TITLE: Reload Action with Data Configuration (AMIS Schema)
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to use the `reload` action with a `data` payload. When the button is clicked, the `date` field will be set to the current time using `NOW()` and sent to the service component with ID `service-reload`. This data will be merged into the target component's data domain before the API request is made.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/service.md#_snippet_29

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
[
  {
    "type": "button",
    "label": "刷新请求",
    "onEvent": {
      "click": {
        "actions": [
          {
            "componentId": "service-reload",
            "actionType": "reload",
            "data": {
              "date": "${NOW()}"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "type": "service",
    "id": "service-reload",
    "name": "service-reload",
    "api": "/api/mock2/number/random",
    "body": "现在是：${random}, 当前时间：${date}"
  }
]
```

