TITLE: Focusing Input-Text Field in Amis Form
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure an Amis form to focus on an input-text field when a button is clicked.  When the '聚焦' button is clicked, the component with the ID `focus_text` will receive focus.
