TITLE: Nested InputKVS Configuration (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This example showcases a nested `input-kvs` configuration, where a second `input-kvs` component is placed inside the `valueItems` of the first. This allows for editing deep data structures. The example creates tables and their columns, with configurable options for each.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-kvs.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    "debug": true,
    "body": [
        {
            "type": "input-kvs",
            "name": "dataModel",
            "addButtonText": "新增表",
            "keyItem": {
              "label": "表名",
              "mode": "horizontal",
               "type": "select",
              "options": [
                  "table1",
                  "table2",
                  "table3"
              ]
            },
            "valueItems": [
                {
                  "type": "input-kvs",
                  "addButtonText": "新增字段",
                  "name": "column",
                  "keyItem": {
                    "label": "字段名",
                    "mode": "horizontal",
                    "type": "select",
                    "options": [
                        "id",
                        "title",
                        "content"
                    ]
                  },
                  "valueItems": [
                      {
                        "type": "switch",
                        "name": "primary",
                        "mode": "horizontal",
                        "label": "是否是主键"
                      },
                      {
                        "type": "select",
                        "name": "type",
                        "label": "字段类型",
                        "mode": "horizontal",
                        "options": [
                          "text",
                          "int",
                          "float"
                        ]
                      }
                  ]
              }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
```

