LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "page",
    "initApi": "/api/mock2/page/initData?keywords=${keywords}",
    "body": [
      {
        "type": "flex",
        "direction": "column",
        "justify": "flex-start",
        "alignItems": "flex-start",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": "search-box",
            "name": "keywords",
            "disabled": true,
            "style": {
              "marginBottom": "10px"
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "search-box",
