TITLE: Radio Usage in Combo - AMIS JSON
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to use the Radio component within a combo component in AMIS.  The combo allows multiple answers to be added, and each answer includes a radio button to indicate if it's the correct answer.  It showcases how the `radio` component can be configured within a combo item.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/radio.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "debug": true,
    data: {
        answers: [
          {
            isAnswer: false,
            answer: '选项 1'
          },
          {
            isAnswer: false,
            answer: '选项 2',
          }
        ]
      },
    "body": [
        {
          type: 'combo',
          label: '可选答案',
          name: 'answers',
          multiple: true,
          addable: true,
          strictMode: false,
          items: [
            {
              type: 'radio',
              name: 'isAnswer',
              columnClassName: 'no-grow'
            },
            {
              type: 'input-text',
              name: 'answer',
              placeholder: '答案文案'
            }
          ]
        },
    ]
}
```

