TITLE: Resetting Checkbox Value using Amis Action in JSON schema
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to reset the Checkbox component to its initial value using the `reset` action. The button triggers the `reset` action on the target checkbox (`componentId: "reset_type"`). If a `resetValue` is configured, the component is reset to that value; otherwise, it resets to the initial value.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/checkbox.md#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "debug": true,
    "body": [
      {
        "type": "checkbox",
        "label": "选项",
        "name": "type",
        "id": "reset_type",
        "option": "选项说明",
        "value": true
      },
        {
            "type": "button",
            "label": "重置",
            "onEvent": {
                "click": {
                    "actions": [
                        {
                            "actionType": "reset",
                            "componentId": "reset_type"
                        }
                    ]
                }
            }
        }
    ]
}
```

