TITLE: Configuring Nested Select to Hide Node Path Labels (Amis, JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This JSON configuration demonstrates how to use the `hideNodePathLabel` property within the Amis nested select component.  When `hideNodePathLabel` is set to true, the select component only displays the label of the currently selected node, hiding the labels of ancestor nodes in the selection. The component is integrated into a form with a mock API endpoint.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/nestedselect.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "debug": true,
  "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "nested-select",
      "name": "nestedSelect",
      "label": "展示已选择节点的祖先节点的文本信息",
      "value": "a,b-1,b-3",
      "multiple": true,
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "value": "a"
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "value": "b",
          "children": [
            {
              "label": "B-1",
              "value": "b-1"
            },
            {
              "label": "B-2",
              "value": "b-2"
            },
            {
              "label": "B-3",
              "value": "b-3"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "value": "c"
        }
      ],
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "type": "nested-select",
      "name": "nestedSelect2",
      "label": "仅展示已选择节点的文本信息",
      "value": "a,b-1,b-3",
      "multiple": true,
      "cascade": true,
      "hideNodePathLabel": true,
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "value": "a"
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "value": "b",
          "children": [
            {
              "label": "B-1",
              "value": "b-1"
            },
            {
              "label": "B-2",
              "value": "b-2"
            },
            {
              "label": "B-3",
              "value": "b-3"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "value": "c"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

