TITLE: Form with Image and QR Code using Control
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates the use of the 'control' component to wrap the image and QR code components. By wrapping these components within a 'control' component, it becomes possible to add labels and descriptions, providing more context to the displayed information. The `body` property of the `control` component contains the component to be wrapped.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/control.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "mode": "horizontal",
  "body": [
    {
        "type": "input-text",
        "label": "文本输入"
    },

    {
        "type": "control",
        "label": "图片",
        body: [
          {
            "type": "image",
            "src": "https://internal-amis-res.cdn.bcebos.com/images/2020-1/1578395692722/4f3cb4202335.jpeg@s_0,w_216,l_1,f_jpg,q_80"
          }
        ]
    },

    {
        "type": "control",
        "label": "二维码",
        "description": "还可以来点描述",
        body: [
          {
              "type": "qr-code",
              "codeSize": 128,
              "backgroundColor": "#108cee",
              "foregroundColor": "#000",
              "value": "https://www.baidu.com"
          }
        ]
    }
  ]
}
```

