TITLE: Panel Body Creator with Context
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet defines a `panelBodyCreator` function that dynamically generates the panel body based on the provided context. It allows creating different form configurations depending on the context, such as whether a button is inside or outside a form.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/extend/editor.md#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
panelBodyCreator = context => {
  console.log(context);
  return [
