TITLE: Removing Expand Button and Using Events (Amis JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This configuration removes the default expand button and uses a custom button with an event handler to trigger row expansion in an Amis `table2` component.  The `expandable.position` is set to `none` to hide the default button, and an `onEvent` handler is attached to a custom button to trigger the `expand` action.
