LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "service",
  "api": "/api/sample?perPage=5",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "table2",
      "source": "$rows",
      "id": "table-select",
      "columns": [
        {
          "title": "Engine",
          "name": "engine"
        },
        {
          "title": "Version",
          "name": "version"
        },
        {
          "title": "Browser",
