TITLE: Pagination Event Handling: Reloading Service - JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates handling pagination `change` event by reloading a service. The `reload` action type is used. The service's data is updated with the new page number. The pagination triggers a service reload.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/pagination.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "service",
    "id": "service_02",
    "api": "/api/mock2/crud/table?page=${page}",
    "data": {
        "page": 1
    },
    "body": [
        {
        "type": "table",
        "title": "表格1",
        "source": "$rows",
        "columns": [
          {
            "name": "engine",
            "label": "Engine"
          },
          {
            "name": "version",
            "label": "Version"
          }
        ]
      },
        {
            "type": "pagination",
            "activePage": "${page}",
            "hasNext": true,
            "onEvent": {
                "change": {
                    "actions": [
                        {
                            "actionType": "reload",
                            "componentId": "service_02",
                            "data": {
                                "page": "${event.data.page}"
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                }
            }
        }
    ]
}
```

