TITLE: Data Mapping with Expanded Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to use the `&` identifier to expand a configured variable in Amis data mapping. By setting a key to `&`, the corresponding variable's value is expanded and merged into the data object.  This reduces boilerplate when including several variables in the data object.
