SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/event-action.md#_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  type: 'page',
  title: '获取页面标题并弹出',
  body: [
    {
      type: 'button',
      className: 'ml-2',
      label: 'toast 页面标题',
      level: 'primary',
      onEvent: {
        click: {
          actions: [
            {
              actionType: 'setEventData',
              args: {
                key: 'title',
                value: '页面标题：${window:document[title]}'
              }
            },
            {
              actionType: 'toast',
              args: {
                msg: '${title}'
              }
            },
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

