TITLE: Configuring Dialog Action
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates configuring a dialog action using an action button. Clicking the button will trigger a modal dialog to appear with specified title and body content. It depends on the amis framework and the `dialog` property is a container where you can define other components. The content displays "Hello World!".
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/action.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "action",
    "label": "弹个框",
    "actionType": "dialog",
    "dialog": {
      "title": "弹框",
      "body": "Hello World!"
    }
}
```

