TITLE: Configuring Button Labels and Icons - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to customize the labels and icons for the add, copy, and edit buttons in the InputTable. The `addBtnLabel`, `addBtnIcon`, `copyBtnLabel`, `copyBtnIcon`, `editBtnLabel`, and `editBtnIcon` properties can be used to change the button appearance.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-table.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
  "body": [
    {
    "type":"input-table",
    "name":"table",
    "addable": true,
    "addBtnLabel": "添加",
    "addBtnIcon": false,
    "copyable": true,
    "copyBtnLabel": "复制",
    "copyBtnIcon": false,
    "editable": true,
    "editBtnLabel": "编辑",
    "editBtnIcon": false,
    "value": [
      {
        "a": "a1",
        "b": "b1"
      }
    ],
    "columns":[
        {
          "name": "a",
          "label": "A"
        },
        {
          "name": "b",
          "label": "B"
        }
    ]
  }
  ]
}
```

