TITLE: Dynamic Data Breadcrumb - Schema
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to configure a Breadcrumb component to use dynamic data from the context using the `source` property. It defines a page with data containing the breadcrumb items and binds them to the Breadcrumb component.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/breadcrumb.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "page",
  "data": {
    "breadcrumb": [
      {
        "label": "首页",
        "href": "https://baidu.gitee.com/"
