TITLE: Markdown Preview with Editor Data Binding
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to use the AMIS markdown component to create a markdown preview using data binding with an editor component.  The editor's `name` is set to "md", and the markdown component's `name` is also set to "md".  This allows the markdown component to dynamically render the content entered in the editor. Requires an AMIS form component and editor component.  Input is markdown text in the editor; output is rendered markdown.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/markdown.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    "body": [
        {
            "type": "group",
            "body": [
                {
                    "type": "editor",
                    "name": "md",
                    "language": "markdown"
                },
                {
                    "type": "markdown",
                    "name": "md"
                }
            ]
        }

    ]
}
```

