TITLE: Tree-Select DeferLoadFinished Event Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This JSON configures a form with a tree-select component that uses lazy loading. It listens for the 'deferLoadFinished' event, triggered when the deferred API request completes successfully. The action displays the result of the API call in a toast message, formatted as a JSON string.  It depends on the Amis framework and requires a backend endpoint at '/api/mock2/form/saveForm' and '/api/mock2/form/deferOptions'.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/treeselect.md#_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
  "debug": true,
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "tree-select",
      "name": "tree",
      "label": "Tree",
      "deferApi": "/api/mock2/form/deferOptions?label=${label}&waitSeconds=2",
      "onEvent": {
        "deferLoadFinished": {
          "actions": [
            {
              "actionType": "toast",
              "args": {
                "msg": "${event.data.result|json}"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "Folder A",
          "value": 1,
          "collapsed": true,
          "children": [
            {
              "label": "file A",
              "value": 2
            },
            {
              "label": "file B",
              "value": 3
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "label": "这下面是懒加载的",
          "value": 4,
          "defer": true
        },
        {
          "label": "file D",
          "value": 5
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

