TITLE: API Request with Conditional Trigger
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure a conditional trigger for an API request used to populate a select component. The `sendOn` property within the `source` configuration of the select component uses an expression `this.a === 2` to determine whether the API request should be triggered when the value of the radio group 'a' changes.  The API is only called when 'a' equals 2.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/linkage.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "title": "",
    "type": "form",
    "mode": "horizontal",
    "body": [
      {
        "label": "选项1",
        "type": "radios",
        "name": "a",
        "inline": true,
        "options": [
          {
            "label": "选项A",
            "value": 1
          },
          {
            "label": "选项B",
            "value": 2
          },
          {
            "label": "选项C",
            "value": 3
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "label": "选项2",
        "type": "select",
        "size": "sm",
        "name": "b",
        "source": {
            "method": "get",
            "url": "/api/mock2/options/level2?a=${a}",
            "sendOn": "this.a === 2"
        },
        "description": "只有<code>选项1</code>选择<code>B</code>的时候，才触发<code>选项2</code>的<code>source</code>接口重新拉取"
      }
    ],
    "actions": []
}
```

