TITLE: Configuring Row Double Click Event in Amis Table2
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema configures the `rowDbClick` event for an Amis Table2 component. When a row is double-clicked, a toast message is displayed showing the row data and index. The table data is fetched from the `/api/mock2/sample` endpoint.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/table2.md#_snippet_67

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "service",
  "api": "/api/mock2/sample?perPage=10",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "table2",
      "source": "$rows",
      "onEvent": {
        "rowDbClick": {
          "actions": [
            {
              "actionType": "toast",
              "args": {
                "msgType": "info",
                "msg": "行双击数据：${event.data.item|json}；行索引：${event.data.index}"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "columns": [
        {
          "name": "id",
          "label": "ID",
          "searchable": true
        },
        {
          "name": "engine",
          "label": "Rendering engine",
          "filterable": {
            "options": [
              "Internet Explorer 4.0",
              "Internet Explorer 5.0"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "browser",
          "label": "Browser",
          "sortable": true
        },
        {
          "name": "platform",
          "label": "Platform(s)"
        },
        {
          "name": "version",
          "label": "Engine version"
        },
        {
          "name": "grade",
          "label": "CSS grade"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

