TITLE: Updating Input Table Cell in Amis Combo using componentName (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates updating a cell within an input-table (nested within a combo) using a dialog. The `componentName` is set to `table` in the `setValue` action, ensuring that only the row currently being edited gets updated.  The `index` is used to target the specific row in the table to update.
