TITLE: Date Input Formula Schema
DESCRIPTION: Defines the schema for a date input control with formula support. Uses `getSchemaTpl` with vertical mode and renders an `input-date` component. Supports expressions or relative values like `now`, `+3days`, `-2weeks`.  Requires a placeholder for static values and specifies a date/time type.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/packages/amis-editor/examples/route/Formula.md#_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: schema
CODE:
```
getSchemaTpl('valueFormula', {
  mode: 'vertical',
  rendererSchema: (schema) => ({
    type: 'input-date',
    ...schema
  }),
  placeholder: '请选择静态值',
  header: '表达式或相对值',
  DateTimeType: 1,
  label: tipedLabel('默认值', '支持例如: <code>now、+3days、-2weeks、+1hour、+2years</code> 等（minute|min|hour|day|week|month|year|weekday|second|millisecond）这种相对值用法')
})
```

