TITLE: Dynamic Data Mapping for Status in Amis Table (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how to use dynamic data mapping with variables in the 'map' and 'labelMap' properties.  The context variables 'statusLabel' and 'statusIcon' are used to dynamically set status labels and icons.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/status.md#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "page",
  "data": {
    "statusLabel": {
      "success": "任务成功",
      "warning": "已停机"
    },
    "statusIcon":  {
      "waiting": "far fa-clock",
      "warning": "fas fa-exclamation"
    }
  },
  "body": {
    "type": "table",
    "data": {
      "items": [
        {
          "id": "1",
          "name": "Task1",
          "status": "success"
        },
        {
          "id": "2",
          "name": "Task2",
          "status": "processing",
        },
        {
          "id": "3",
          "name": "Task3",
          "status": "waiting",
        },
        {
          "id": "4",
          "name": "Task4",
          "status": "warning",
        },
        {
          "id": "5",
          "name": "Task5",
          "status": "fail",
        }
      ]
    },
    "columns": [
      {
        "name": "id",
        "label": "ID"
      },
      {
        "name": "name",
        "label": "Name"
      },
      {
        "name": "status",
        "label": "状态",
        "type": "mapping",
        "map": {
          "*": {
            "type": "status",
            "map": {
              "processing": "rolling",
              "waiting": "${statusIcon.waiting}",
              "warning": "${statusIcon.warning}"
            },
            "labelMap": {
              "success": "${statusLabel.success}",
              "processing": "处理中",
              "waiting": "等待中",
              "warning": "${statusLabel.warning}"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

