TITLE: Data Mapping with Array Value Extraction
DESCRIPTION: This example showcases how to extract values from an array in Amis data mapping using the `$table` syntax.  It retrieves specified variables from each item in the `table` array and creates a new array with only those variables.  This feature allows restructuring array data for API requests.
