TITLE: Auto-filling in Multi-select Image Component
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates auto-filling with a multi-select image component. It uses the `items` variable and the `pick` function to extract the `url` from each selected item in the `image` component. It also uses the `last` function to extract the URL from the last selected item.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-image.md#_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "debug": true,
  "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "input-image",
      "name": "image",
      "label": "image",
      "multiple": true,
      "receiver": "/api/upload/file",
      "autoFill": {
        "myUrl": "${items|pick:url}",
        "lastUrl": "${items|last|pick:url}"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tpl",
      "label": false,
      "inline": false,
      "tpl": "<strong>myUrl集合</strong>"
    },
    {
      "type": "each",
      "name": "myUrl",
      "className": "mb-1",
      "items": {
        "type": "tpl",
        "tpl": "<span class='label label-info m-l-sm inline-block mb-1'>${item}</span>"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tpl",
      "label": false,
      "inline": false,
      "tpl": "<strong>lastUrl</strong>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "name": "lastUrl",
      "label": "lastUrl",
      "inline": false
    }
  ]
}
```

