DESCRIPTION: This CSS snippet demonstrates how to embed custom fonts (Wingdings and Symbol) for rendering list symbols correctly in the office-viewer component in Amis.  This is useful to avoid list rendering issues. It defines the `@font-face` rules for both Wingdings and Symbol fonts, specifying the font family and the URL to the font files. This ensures that the correct glyphs are used for list bullets, preventing potential garbled or incorrect characters.
