TITLE: Using Data Provider with Event Triggers in Amis Service
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates using the `dataProvider` property with event triggers to update the component's data based on specific events, such as `inited` and `onApiFetched`. It showcases how to modify data using `setData` in response to these events.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/service.md#_snippet_22

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "service",
    "api": "/api/mock2/page/initData",
    "dataProvider": {
        "inited": "setData({ addedNumber: data.number + 1  })",
        "onApiFetched": "setData({ year: new Date(data.date).getFullYear(),  })"
    },
    "data": {
        "number": 8887
    },
    "body": {
        "type": "panel",
        "title": "$title",
        "body": [
            {
                "type": "tpl",
                "wrapperComponent": "p",
                "tpl": "静态数字为：<strong>${addedNumber}</strong>"
            },
            {
                "type": "tpl",
                "wrapperComponent": "p",
                "tpl": "接口返回值的日期为：<strong>${date}</strong>"
            },
            {
                "type": "tpl",
                "wrapperComponent": "p",
                "tpl": "接口返回值的年份为：<strong>${year}</strong>"
            },
        ]
    }
}
```

