TITLE: Configuring Wait Action with Amis Schema
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure the 'wait' action type in an Amis schema. This action pauses the execution of subsequent actions for a specified duration (in milliseconds). The `time` property sets the waiting period.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/event-action.md#_snippet_17

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  type: 'page',
  title: '3 秒后 toast 页面标题',
  body: [
    {
      type: 'button',
      className: 'ml-2',
      label: 'toast 页面标题',
      level: 'primary',
      onEvent: {
        click: {
          actions: [
