TITLE: Configuring Search Action for Input-Tree (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This JSON snippet configures a `search-box` to filter an `input-tree`.  On `change` event on search box a search action is triggered on the `input-tree`. The tree with the id "tree" will be filtered based on the keyword entered in the search box. The value of the search box is passed as the keyword argument to the search action.
