TITLE: Recursive Definition for Tree Structure (JSON Schema)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to create a recursive definition to allow infinite-level editing of data structures.  It defines a `combo` component named 'options' that contains several items, including a reference to itself (`$ref: "options"`) to create a tree-like structure.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/types/definitions.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "definitions": {
          "options": {
            "type": "combo",
            "multiple": true,
            "multiLine": true,
            "name": "options",
            "items": [
            {
                "type": "group",
                "body": [
                {
                    "label": "名称",
                    "name": "label",
                    "type": "input-text",
                    "required": true
                },
                {
                    "label": "值",
                    "name": "value",
                    "type": "input-text",
                    "required": true
                }
                ]
            },
            {
                "label": "包含子选项",
                "type": "switch",
                "name": "hasChildren",
                "mode": "inline",
                "className": "block"
            },
            {
                "$ref": "options",
                "label": "子选项",
                "name": "children",
                "visibleOn": "this.hasOwnProperty('hasChildren') && this.hasChildren",
                "addButtonText": "新增子选项"
            }
            ]
        }
      },
      "type": "page",
      "title": "引用",
      "body": [
          {
              "type": "form",
              "api": "api/xxx",
              "actions": [],
              "body": [
                  {
                      "$ref": "options",
                      "label": "选项"
                  },

                  {
                      "type": "static",
                      "label": "当前值",
                      "tpl": "<pre>${options|json}</pre>"
                  }
              ]
          }
      ]
}
```

