TITLE: Nested FieldSets - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This snippet showcases how to nest FieldSet components within each other. This allows for creating complex hierarchical groupings of form items. Both the outer and inner FieldSets are configured to be collapsible, with the inner one initially collapsed and a base size.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/fieldset.md#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "fieldSet",
      "title": "基本配置",
      "collapsable": true,
      "body": [
        {
          "name": "text1",
          "type": "input-text",
          "label": "文本1"
        },

        {
          "name": "text2",
          "type": "input-text",
          "label": "文本2"
        },

        {
          "type": "fieldSet",
          "title": "基本配置",
          "collapsable": true,
          "collapsed": true,
          size: 'base',
          "body": [
            {
              "name": "text1",
              "type": "input-text",
              "label": "文本1"
            },

            {
              "name": "text2",
              "type": "input-text",
              "label": "文本2"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

