TITLE: Log Component Polling Configuration in Schema
DESCRIPTION: This schema configuration uses the Service component's polling capability to fetch log data. It defines an API endpoint, polling interval, and a condition to stop polling. The `concatDataFields` property concatenates the returned log messages, and the log component displays the combined log data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/log.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: schema
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "page",
  "title": "轮询日志演示，当秒钟到 59 时会停止轮询",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "service",
      "api": {
        "method": "get",
        "url": "/api/mock2/log/date?offset=${offset}",
        "autoRefresh": false, // 因为设置了轮询，所以关闭自动刷新
        "concatDataFields": "log"
      },
      "silentPolling": true,
      "interval": 1000,
      "stopAutoRefreshWhen": "${finished}",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "log",
          "height": 300,
          "source": "${log}"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

