TITLE: Sending HTTP Requests with AJAX Action (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema demonstrates sending an HTTP request using the 'ajax' action. A button is configured to trigger an AJAX request to a specified URL when clicked. The `api` property defines the request details, including URL, method, and response messages.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/event-action.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: json
