TITLE: Form Component with Renderer Decorator
DESCRIPTION: This JSX code shows the implementation of a Form component in AMIS using the Renderer decorator. The 'type' property in the decorator specifies the component type. The render function renders the form, iterating through the body elements (form items) and rendering each one using the 'render' prop.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/extend/internal.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
@Renderer({
  type: 'form'
  // ... 其他信息隐藏了
})
export class FormRenderer extends React.Component {
  // ... 其他信息隐藏了
  render() {
    const {
      title,
      body,
      render // 用来渲染孩子节点，如果当前是叶子节点则可以忽略。
    } = this.props;
    return (
      <form className="form">
        {body.map((control, index) => (
          <div className="form-item" key={index}>
            {render(`${index}/control`, control)}
          </div>
        ))}
      </form>
    );
  }
}
```

