TITLE: NestedSelect: Multiple Leaf Node Selection w/ Cascade in Amis JSON
DESCRIPTION: This snippet configures a multi-select NestedSelect that allows only leaf node selection while also enabling cascading selection. `onlyLeaf` ensures only leaf nodes can be chosen, and `cascade` prevents automatic selection of child nodes when a parent is selected. `multiple` allows for multiple selections.
