DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to handle the 'mouseleave' event of the Tpl component in Amis. When the mouse leaves the Tpl component, a toast notification is displayed showing the type of the native event. Requires the Amis framework and assumes a toast action is configured.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/tpl.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
   "type": "tpl",
    "tpl": "Hello",
    "onEvent": {
        "mouseleave": {
        "actions": [
            {
            "actionType": "toast",
            "args": {
                "msgType": "info",
                "msg": "${event.context.nativeEvent.type}"
            }
            }
        ]
        }
    }
}
```

