TITLE: Reload Action in Amis Form
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema defines an Amis form with a list-select component and a button to reload the component's data source. The 'reload' action, triggered by the button's 'click' event, refreshes the data source for the component with the ID 'reload_type'. This is particularly useful for updating the list of options in the selector based on changes in the underlying data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/matrix-checkboxes.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "debug": true,
    "body": [
        {
          "type": "list-select",
          "name": "select",
          "label": "单选",
          "clearable": true,
          "id": "reload_type",
          "source": "/api/mock2/form/getOptions?waitSeconds=1",
          "value": "a"
        },
        {
            "type": "button",
            "label": "重新加载",
            "onEvent": {
                "click": {
                    "actions": [
                        {
                            "actionType": "reload",
                            "componentId": "reload_type"
                        }
                    ]
                }
            }
        }
    ]
}
```

