TITLE: IsEquals Filter with Data Field Variables
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates using `isEquals` with variables from the data context for the `equalsValue`, `notequalsValue` parameters.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/data-mapping.md#_snippet_77

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "page",
  "data": {
    "text1": "Hello",
    "text2": "hello",
    "equalsValue": "这个值等于'Hello'",
    "notequalsValue": "这个值不等于'Hello'"
  },
  "body": [
    {
        "type": "tpl",
        "tpl": "${text1|isEquals:'Hello':equalsValue:notequalsValue}" // 输出: 等于
    },
    {
        "type": "divider"
    },
    {
        "type": "tpl",
        "tpl": "${text2|isEquals:'Hello':equalsValue:notequalsValue}" // 输出: 等于
    }
  ]
}
```

