TITLE: Handling Tag Mouseenter Event with Amis
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to handle the 'mouseenter' event of a Tag component and display a toast message with the event details. It utilizes the 'onEvent' property and accesses the event context to retrieve the native event type and label.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/tag.md#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
   "type": "tag",
    "label": "success",
    "displayMode": "normal",
    "color": "success",
    "onEvent": {
        "mouseenter": {
        "actions": [
            {
            "actionType": "toast",
            "args": {
                "msgType": "info",
