TITLE: InputFile AutoFill Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This demonstrates how to automatically populate other form fields with data received from the upload API response using the `autoFill` property.  It maps the `url` from the upload response to the `myUrl` text input field. Requires a "url" key present in the API response data.
