LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "input-file",
      "name": "file",
      "label": "File",
      "accept": "*",
      "receiver": "/api/upload/file",
      "autoFill": {
        "myUrl": "${url}"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "input-text",
      "name": "myUrl",
      "label": "url"
    }
  ]
}
