TITLE: Dialog Confirm Event Configuration with JSON
DESCRIPTION: This JSON snippet configures a button that opens a dialog and defines an action to be executed when the dialog's "confirm" event is triggered (e.g., when a user clicks a "confirm" button within the dialog).  It uses the `onEvent` property within the dialog configuration to specify actions for the `confirm` event, displaying a toast message with the value of the 'name' field from the dialog's form.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/dialog.md#_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
[
  {
    "label": "弹个框",
    "type": "button",
    "onEvent": {
      "click": {
        "actions": [
          {
            "actionType": "dialog",
            "dialog": {
              "title": "一个弹框",
              "body": [
                {
                  "type": "alert",
                  "body": "试试点击确认按钮",
                  "level": "info",
                  "className": "mb-1"
                },
                {
                  "type": "form",
                  "title": "表单",
                  "debug": true,
                  "body": [
                    {
                      "label": "你的名字",
                      "type": "input-text",
                      "name": "name",
                      "id": "u:00ef9e3fe9db",
                      "mode": "horizontal",
                      "size": "md",
                      "value": "Amis"
                    }
                  ],
                  "id": "u:f4b2a90b685b"
                }
              ],
              "onEvent": {
                "confirm": {
                    "actions": [
                      {
                          "actionType": "toast",
                          "args": {
                              "msg": "你的名字是${name}"
                          }
                      }
                    ]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  }
]
```

