TITLE: Combo with Multi-Line Display
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how to configure the Combo component to display its items in multiple lines. The `multiLine` property is set to `true` to achieve this layout. This improves readability when the combo contains many items or items with long labels.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/combo.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "mode": "horizontal",
  "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "combo",
      "name": "combo1",
      "label": "Combo 单行展示",
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "text",
          "label": "文本",
          "type": "input-text"
        },
        {
          "name": "select",
          "label": "选项",
          "type": "select",
          "options": ["a", "b", "c"]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
        "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "type": "combo",
      "name": "combo2",
      "label": "Combo 多行展示",
      "multiLine": true,
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "text",
          "label": "文本",
          "type": "input-text"
        },
        {
          "name": "select",
          "label": "选项",
          "type": "select",
          "options": ["a", "b", "c"]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

