TITLE: Configuring AMIS Table ClearAll Action
DESCRIPTION: This configuration sets up a button toolbar to trigger the `clearAll` action on an AMIS table.  The `clearAll` action deselects all rows of the table.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/table2.md#_snippet_74

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
[
  {
    "type": "button-toolbar",
    "className": "m-b",
    "buttons": [
      {
        "name": "trigger3",
        "id": "trigger3",
        "type": "action",
        "label": "清空表格全部选中项",
        "onEvent": {
        "click": {
            "actions": [
              {
                "actionType": "clearAll",
                "componentId": "table-select",
                "description": "点击设置指定表格全部选中项清空"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "service",
    "api": "/api/mock2/sample?perPage=10",
    "body": [
      {
        "id": "table-select",
        "type": "table2",
        "source": "$rows",
        "selectable": true,
        "multiple": true,
        "columns": [
          {
            "name": "id",
            "label": "ID"
          },
          {
            "name": "browser",
            "label": "Browser"
          },
          {
            "name": "version",
            "label": "Version"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
]
```

