TITLE: Customizing Pop-over Trigger and Appearance - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This snippet customizes the pop-over trigger and appearance. It sets the `trigger` to `hover`, removes the pop-over icon (`showIcon: false`), positions the pop-over, and uses a template to display the browser information.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/table2.md#_snippet_44

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "service",
  "api": "/api/sample?perPage=6",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "table2",
      "source": "$rows",
      "columns": [
        {
          "title": "Engine",
          "name": "engine"
        },
        {
          "title": "Version",
          "name": "version"
        },
        {
          "type": "tpl",
          "title": "Browser",
          "name": "browser",
          "tpl": "${engine|truncate:5}",
          "popOver": {
            "trigger": "hover",
            "position": "left-top",
            "showIcon": false,
            "body": {
              "type": "tpl",
              "tpl": "${browser}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "title": "Badge",
          "name": "badgeText"
        },
        {
          "title": "Platform",
          "name": "platform"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

