TITLE: Configuring Copy Action with Amis Schema
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure the 'copy' action type in an Amis schema. The action copies specified content (either plain text or rich text) to the clipboard. The `env.copy` method needs to be implemented for this action to work.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/event-action.md#_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  type: 'page',
  body: [
    {
      type: 'button',
      label: '复制一段文本',
      level: 'primary',
      className: 'mr-2',
      onEvent: {
        click: {
          actions: [
            {
              actionType: 'copy',
              args: {
                content: 'http://www.baidu.com'
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      type: 'button',
      label: '复制一段富文本',
      level: 'primary',
      onEvent: {
        click: {
          actions: [
            {
              actionType: 'copy',
              args: {
                copyFormat: 'text/html',
                content: "<a href='http://www.baidu.com'>link</a> <b>bold</b>"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

