TITLE: InputText Value Transformation - Amis
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to automatically transform the input value of the `input-text` component. The `transform` property allows specifying transformations like converting to lowercase (`lowerCase`) or uppercase (`upperCase`).  The first component converts input to lower case but does not transform the dropdown selection. The form submits to an unspecified endpoint and is in debug mode.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-text.md#_snippet_10

LANGUAGE: JSON
