SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-datetime-range.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    "body": [
        {
            "type": "input-datetime-range",
            "name": "select",
            "label": "日期范围",
            "shortcuts": "today,yesterday,1dayago,7daysago"
        }
    ]
}
```

