TITLE: Formula Solving Floating Point Issues in Amis
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how the formula component, particularly with the new expression syntax, addresses floating-point calculation issues. It compares the direct sum of two numbers with the sum calculated by the formula component, showcasing the improved accuracy.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/formula.md#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "input-number",
      "name": "a",
      "value": 0.1,
      "label": "A"
    },
    {
      "type": "input-number",
      "name": "b",
      "value": 0.2,
      "label": "B"
    },
    {
      "type": "input-number",
      "name": "sum",
      "label": "直接相加",
      "disabled": true
    },
    {
      "type": "formula",
      "name": "sum",
      "formula": "a + b"
    },
    {
      "type": "input-number",
      "name": "sum-new",
      "label": "使用新表达式",
      "disabled": true
    },
    {
      "type": "formula",
      "name": "sum-new",
      "formula": "${a + b}"
    }
  ]
}
```

