TITLE: Reloading Selector Data Source - Amis JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema demonstrates how to reload the data source of a 'button-group-select' component using the 'reload' action.  The 'button-group-select' component is configured with a 'source' attribute pointing to an API endpoint. Clicking the '重新加载' button triggers the 'reload' action, fetching the latest data from the API and updating the component's options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/button-group-select.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "debug": true,
    "body": [
        {
          "type": "button-group-select",
          "label": "选项",
          "name": "type",
          "id": "reload_type",
          "source": "/api/mock2/form/getOptions?waitSeconds=1"
        },
        {
            "type": "button",
            "label": "重新加载",
            "onEvent": {
                "click": {
                    "actions": [
                        {
                            "actionType": "reload",
                            "componentId": "reload_type"
                        }
                    ]
                }
            }
        }
    ]
}
```

