TITLE: Custom Match Function Interface
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript interface describes the signature of a custom match function (`matchFunc`) used for filtering data in the AMIS CRUD component when `loadDataOnce` is enabled.  The interface defines the parameters passed to the function, including the full dataset, the most recent raw data from the API, and configuration options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/crud.md#_snippet_47

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
interface CRUDMatchFunc {
  (
    /* 当前列表的全量数据 */
    items: any,
    /* 最近一次接口返回的全量数据 */
    itemsRaw: any,
    /** 相关配置 */
    options?: {
      /* 查询参数 */
      query: Record<string, any>;
      /* 列配置 */
      columns: any;
      /** match-sorter 匹配函数 */
      matchSorter: (
        items: any[],
        value: string,
        options?: MatchSorterOptions<any>
      ) => any[];
    }
  ): boolean;
}
```

