TITLE: Setting Margin Bottom CSS Utility Classes
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines CSS utility classes for setting the bottom margin of an element. It includes classes for positive, negative, and zero values, using a scale based on rem units. The classes allow developers to quickly apply specific margin bottom values without writing custom CSS rules.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/packages/amis-ui/scss/helper/spacing/_margin.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: CSS
