TITLE: VLOOKUP with IFERROR Handling
DESCRIPTION: This formula performs a VLOOKUP to find a matching value in the TABLA_AHORRO table. It uses IFERROR to return an empty string if the lookup fails. It looks up the value in cell A4 within the TABLA_AHORRO table and returns the value from the 6th column. The result will be the matching value or an empty string if not found.
