TITLE: Resetting Form Component Value - Amis JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema defines a form with a 'button-group-select' component and a 'reset' button. When the 'reset' button is clicked, it triggers the 'reset' action on the specified component, reverting its value to the initial value or the configured 'resetValue'.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/button-group-select.md#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "debug": true,
  "data": {
    "abc": {
      "type": "c"
    }
  },
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "button-group-select",
      "label": "选项",
      "name": "type",
      "id": "reset_type",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "Option A",
          "value": "a"
        },
        {
          "label": "Option B",
          "value": "b"
        },
        {
          "label": "Option C",
          "value": "c"
        }
      ],
      "value": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "button",
      "label": "重置",
      "onEvent": {
        "click": {
          "actions": [
            {
              "actionType": "reset",
              "componentId": "reset_type"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

