TITLE: FormItem Conditional Disable JSON
DESCRIPTION: This code configures the `disabledOn` property to conditionally disable a FormItem component based on a specified expression. In this example, the '文本' input field is disabled when the '数量' input field's value is greater than 1. This provides dynamic control over form element interaction based on user input.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/formitem.md#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "input-number",
      "label": "数量",
      "name": "number",
      "value": 0,
      "description": "调整数量大小查看效果吧！"
    },
    {
      "type": "input-text",
      "label": "文本",
      "name": "text",
      "disabledOn": "this.number > 1",
      "description": "当数量大于1的时候，该文本框会被禁用"
    }
  ]
}
```

