TITLE: PDF Viewer with File Upload
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates how to integrate the PDF Viewer with an `input-file` component in Amis. By assigning the same `name` attribute to both the `input-file` and `pdf-viewer` components, the PDF Viewer automatically displays the PDF file selected via the file upload. The `asBlob` property in `input-file` ensures the file is handled as a binary large object.
