TITLE: Conditional Pop-over using popOverEnableOn - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to conditionally enable the pop-over based on an expression.  The `popOverEnableOn` property is set to `this.id == 1`, so the pop-over will only be active for rows where the `id` is equal to 1.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/table2.md#_snippet_46

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "service",
  "api": "/api/sample?perPage=6",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "table2",
      "source": "$rows",
      "columns": [
        {
          "title": "ID",
          "name": "id",
          "popOver": {
            "body": {
              "type": "tpl",
              "tpl": "${id}"
            }
          },
          "popOverEnableOn": "this.id == 1"
        },
        {
          "title": "Engine",
