TITLE: Select Input Formula Schema
DESCRIPTION: Defines the schema for an options-based input control (select) with formula support. Configures a select component using `getSchemaTpl`, setting its options.  It removes the `source` property, preventing automatic data fetching. The visibility is controlled by `this.selectFirst !== true && this.source != null`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/packages/amis-editor/examples/route/Formula.md#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: schema
CODE:
```
getSchemaTpl('valueFormula', {
  rendererSchema: (schema) => ({
    ...schema,
    type: 'select',
    options: [
      {
        label: '选项1',
        value: '1'
      },
      {
        label: '选项2',
        value: '2'
      }
    ]
  }),
  // 默认值组件设计有些问题，自动发起了请求，接口数据作为了默认值选项，接口形式应该是设置静态值或者FX
  needDeleteProps: ['source'],
  // 当数据源是自定义静态选项时，不额外配置默认值，在选项上直接勾选即可，放开会有个bug：当去掉勾选时，默认值配置组件不清空，只是schema清空了value
  visibleOn: 'this.selectFirst !== true && this.source != null'
})
```

