TITLE: Summing a Range of Columns with Current Row Reference
DESCRIPTION: These formulas compute the sum across a range of columns, 'Jan' to 'Feb', in the 'Sales' table for the current row indicated by '@'. The first formula uses the column range referencing within the table. The second uses specific references. They give the same result; the sum of January and February in the current row.
