TITLE: Raw Filter Data Mapping
DESCRIPTION: This code illustrates how to use the `raw` filter in Amis to display original, unescaped text.  When Amis applies `html` filter by default, `raw` can be used to avoid that.  However, this should be used with caution as it can introduce XSS vulnerabilities if the data is untrusted.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/data-mapping.md#_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: schema
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "page",
  "data": {
    "html": "<div>这是一段<code>html</code></div>"
  },
  "body": {
    "type": "tpl",
    "tpl": "html is: ${html|raw}"
  }
}
```

