LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "page",
  "data": {
    "name": "zhangsan"
  },
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "tpl",
      "tpl": "my name is ${name}"
    },
    {
      "type": "container",
      "data": {
        "name": "lisi"
      },
      "body":  {
        "type": "tpl",
        "tpl": "my name is ${name}"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

