TITLE: Configuring Custom Field Type in Condition Builder
DESCRIPTION: This configuration demonstrates how to define a custom field type within the Amis Condition Builder. It uses the `custom` type and specifies an `input-color` component for the field's value. It also defines the operators and a default value for the custom field. The `operators` array allows specifying the available comparison types for that field.
