TITLE: Configuring Dialog Action with Amis Button (JSON)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure a dialog action for an Amis Button component. It sets the actionType to "dialog" and defines the dialog content, including a form with a text input field. The form's API endpoint is specified for saving the form data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/action.md#_snippet_17

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "label": "Dialog Form",
  "type": "button",
  "level": "primary",
  "actionType": "dialog",
  "dialog": {
    "title": "表单设置",
    "body": {
      "type": "form",
      "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "input-text",
          "name": "text",
          "label": "文本"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

