TITLE: Multi-Select with Select All in Amis Select
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to enable the 'Select All' functionality in a multi-select component using the `checkAll` property. The `checkAllBySearch` property determines whether 'Select All' selects all items or only the filtered items during a search. By default, `checkAllBySearch` is true from version 2.8.1.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/select.md#_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "body": [
        {
            "label": "多选",
            "type": "select",
            "name": "select2",
            "searchable": true,
            "checkAll": true,
            "multiple": true,
            "clearable": true,
            "source": "/api/mock2/form/getOptions"
        }
    ]
}
```

