TITLE: Dynamic Property Table Source - JSON
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to dynamically generate the entire property table based on data from a 'source' property.  The 'source' property is set to `${items}`, which references an array of objects within the 'data' object. The 'title' is also dynamically set. This setup makes it possible to entirely define the property table from a data source.
