TITLE: Configuring Custom Validation Error Messages with Parameters in AMIS Form
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to configure custom validation error messages that include parameters from the validation configuration, using `$1`. The `text` field is validated to be numeric with a minimum value of 10, and the error message includes this minimum value.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/formitem.md#_snippet_36

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "input-text",
      "label": "文本",
      "name": "text",
      "validations": {
        "isNumeric": true,
        "minimum": 10
      },
      "validationErrors": {
        "minimum": "同学，最少输入$1以上的数字哈"
      },
      "description": "请输入数字类型文本"
