SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/picker.md#_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
                "type": "button",
                "icon": "fa fa-times text-danger",
                "actionType": "ajax",
                "confirmText": "您确认要删除?",
                "api": "delete:/api/mock2/sample/$id"
              }
```

