TITLE: Grid 2D Layout with Custom Gaps - JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema demonstrates how to configure the spacing between grid items in a Grid 2D layout using the `gap` and `gapRow` properties. The `gap` property sets both horizontal and vertical spacing, while `gapRow` specifically adjusts the vertical spacing between rows.
