TITLE: FieldSet Style for Collapse in Form
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how to enable FieldSet style for Collapse when used within a Form.  The `enableFieldSetStyle` property controls the appearance of the Collapse component, making it resemble a FieldSet. The value is bound to a switch to control style.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/collapse.md#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: schema
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "form",
  "body": [
    {
      "type": "switch",
      "name": "enableFieldSetStyle",
      "label": "切换展示方式",
      "mode": "horizontal",
      "value": true
    },
    {
      "type": "collapse-group",
      "activeKey": ["1"],
      "enableFieldSetStyle": "${enableFieldSetStyle}",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "collapse",
          "key": "1",
          "header": "标题1",
          "body": "这里是内容1"
        },
        {
          "type": "collapse",
          "key": "2",
          "header": "标题2",
          "body": "这里是内容2"
        },
        {
          "type": "collapse",
          "key": "3",
          "header": "标题3",
          "body": "这里是内容3"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

