TITLE: Static Color Display in Amis Form
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to display a color value statically within an Amis Form using the `static-color` component. The form's `data` property holds the color value, and the `static-color` component's `name` attribute maps it to the corresponding variable in the form's data.  The `label` attribute specifies the label displayed next to the color.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/color.md#_snippet_2

