TITLE: Dynamically Controlling Spinner Rendering - Amis Schema
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to dynamically control the rendering of the Spinner component using the `showOn` property. The `showOn` property accepts an expression that determines whether the spinner should be visible based on the state of other components.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/spinner.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: schema
CODE:
```
{
  type: 'page',
  body: {
    type: 'form',
    body: [
      {
        type: 'switch',
        name: 'show',
        label: 'show',
        value: true
      },
      {
        type: 'spinner',
        overlay: false,
        showOn: 'this.show'
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

