TITLE: Reloading Input-Text Field with Source in Amis Form
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to configure an Amis form to reload the data source of an input-text field when a button is clicked. This feature is available only for the selector mode, where the component is configured with a `source`. The '重新加载' button triggers the reload action for the component with the ID `reload_text`, fetching data from the configured `source` URL.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-text.md#_snippet_21

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "debug": true,
    "body": [
        {
            "name": "text",
            "id": "reload_text",
            "type": "input-text",
            "label": "text",
            "value": "a",
            "source": "/api/mock2/form/getOptions?waitSeconds=1"
        },
        {
            "type": "button",
            "label": "重新加载",
            "onEvent": {
                "click": {
                    "actions": [
                        {
                            "actionType": "reload",
                            "componentId": "reload_text"
                        }
                    ]
                }
            }
        }
    ]
}
```

