TITLE: TPL Component with VisibleOn Expression (Amis)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet showcases the use of a visibleOn expression with a TPL (Template) component in Amis. The template will only be visible if the 'show' variable in the current scope is equal to 1. It demonstrates basic conditional rendering.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/concepts/expression.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "tpl",
  "tpl": "当前作用域中变量 show 是 1 的时候才可以看得到我哦~",
  "visibleOn": "${show === 1}"
}
```

