TITLE: Basic Grid 2D Layout Configuration - JSON Schema
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema defines a basic Grid 2D layout with four grid items. Each item specifies its x and y coordinates, height (h), width (w), and a template (tpl) for rendering content within the grid cell. The `gridClassName` property allows for applying custom CSS classes to each grid item.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/grid-2d.md#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "grid-2d",
  "grids": [
    {
      "x": 1,
      "y": 1,
      "h": 1,
      "w": 6,
      "gridClassName": "bg-green-300",
      "type": "tpl",
      "tpl": "[grid-1] x:1 y:1 h:1 w:6"
    },
    {
      "x": 7,
      "y": 1,
      "h": 1,
      "w": 6,
      "gridClassName": "bg-blue-300",
      "type": "tpl",
      "tpl": "[grid-2] x:7 y:1 h:1 w:6"
    },
    {
      "x": 1,
      "y": 2,
      "h": 2,
      "w": 4,
      "gridClassName": "bg-red-300",
      "type": "tpl",
      "tpl": "[grid-3] x:1 y:2 h:2 w:4"
    },
    {
      "x": 5,
      "y": 2,
      "h": 1,
      "w": 8,
      "gridClassName": "bg-purple-300",
      "type": "tpl",
      "tpl": "[grid-4] x:5 y:2 h:1 w:8"
    }
  ]
}
```

