TITLE: Expression Shortcut Example
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to use expressions to define custom date shortcuts.  It defines a shortcut '前天' using a DATEMODIFY expression.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/input-datetime.md#_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "debug": true,
    "api": "/api/mock2/form/saveForm",
    "body": [
        {
            "type": "input-datetime",
            "name": "datetime",
            "label": "日期",
            "shortcuts": [
                {
                    "label": "前天",
                    "date": "${STARTOF(DATEMODIFY(NOW(), -2, 'day'))}"
                },
                "yesterday",
                "today"
            ]
        }
    ]
}
```

