TITLE: Configuring Checkboxes Delete Confirm Event
DESCRIPTION: This JSON schema configures the 'deleteConfirm' event on a removable checkboxes component. When an option is deleted and confirmed, a toast notification shows the deleted item's JSON representation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/form/checkboxes.md#_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "form",
    "debug": true,
    "body": [
      {
        "name": "checkboxes",
        "type": "checkboxes",
        "label": "复选框",
        "removable": true,
        "labelField": "label2",
        "valueField": "value2",
        "options": [
          {
            "label2": "OptionA",
            "value2": "a"
          },
          {
            "label2": "OptionB",
            "value2": "b"
          },
          {
            "label2": "OptionC",
            "value2": "c"
          },
          {
            "label2": "OptionD",
            "value2": "d"
          }
        ],
        "onEvent": {
            "deleteConfirm": {
            "actions": [
                {
                "actionType": "toast",
                    "args": {
                        "msg": "${event.data.item|json}"
                    }
                }
            ]
            }
        }
      }
    ]
  }
```

