SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/table-view.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "table-view",
  "trs": [
    {
      "background": "#F7F7F7",
      "tds": [
        {
          "body": {
            "type": "tpl",
            "tpl": "地区"
          }
        },
        {
          "body": {
            "type": "tpl",
            "tpl": "城市"
          }
        },
        {
          "body": {
            "type": "tpl",
            "tpl": "销量"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tds": [
        {
          "body": {
            "type": "tpl",
            "tpl": ""
          },
          "style": {
            "borderBottomWidth": 0,
            "borderLeftWidth": 0
          }
        },
        {
          "body": {
            "type": "tpl",
            "tpl": "北京"
          }
        },
        {
          "body": {
            "type": "tpl",
            "tpl": ""
          },
          "style": {
            "borderBottomWidth": 0,
            "borderRightWidth": 0
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

