TITLE: Initializing Timeline with Card Display (AMIS)
DESCRIPTION: This initializes an AMIS timeline component that displays its content within cards. It utilizes `cardSchema` to define the structure of the cards, including header details like title, subtitle, description, and avatar. The timeline items include data to populate the cards and a detailed description for one of the entries.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/timeline.md#_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
  "type": "page",
  "body": [
    {
      type: 'timeline',
      mode: 'alternate',
      direction: 'horizontal',
      items: [
        {
          cardSchema: {
            type: 'card',
            href: 'https://github.com/baidu/amis',
            header: {
              title: '标题',
              subTitle: '副标题',
              description: '这是一段描述',
              avatarText: 'AMIS'
            },
            body: '这里是内容'
          }
        },
        {
          time: '2019-02-08',
          cardSchema: {
            type: 'card',
            href: 'https://github.com/baidu/amis',
            header: {
              title: '标题',
              subTitle: '副标题',
              description: '这是一段描述',
              avatarText: 'AMIS'
            },
            body: '这里是内容'
          }
        },
        {
          time: '2019-02-09',
          title: '表格展现说明',
          detail:
            '通过表格的方式来展现数据，和 table 的不同之处：数据源要求不同：table 的数据源需要是多行的数据，最典型的就是来自某个数据库的表，table view 的数据源可以来自各种固定的数据，比如单元格的某一列是来自某个变量。功能不同：table 只能用来做数据表的展现，table view 除了展现复杂的报表，还能用来进行布局。合并单元格方式不同：table 的合并单元格需要依赖数据，table view 的合并单元格是手动指定的，因此可以支持不规则的数据格式。'
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

