TITLE: TypeScript Interface for ListBodyField
DESCRIPTION: Defines the structure of the `ListBodyField` interface used within the Amis List component. It specifies optional properties for label, CSS class names (outer, label, inner), field name binding, pop-over configuration, quick edit functionality, and copyable feature. This interface is used for configuring the body content within each list item.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/list.md#_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
interface ListBodyField {
  /* 列标题 */
  label?: string;
  /* 外层DOM的CSS类名 */
  className?: string;
  /* label的CSS类名 */
  labelClassName?: string;
  /* 内层组件的CSS类名，className属性会添加到外层DOM，如果要在组件层级添加CSS类，请设置当前属性 */
  innerClassName?: string;
  /* 绑定字段名 */
  name?: string;
  /* 配置查看详情功能 */
  popOver?: SchemaPopOver;
  /* 配置快速编辑功能 */
  quickEdit?: SchemaQuickEdit;
  /* 配置点击复制功能 */
  copyable?: SchemaCopyable;
}
```

