TITLE: IFrame Height Adaptation - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet shows how to send the iFrame's height to the Amis environment using the `amis:resize` event. This allows the Amis container to dynamically adjust the iFrame's height for better responsiveness.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/iframe.md#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
