TITLE: VLOOKUP with MATCH
DESCRIPTION: This formula performs a VLOOKUP to find a matching value in the 'Vertices' table, using the 'ID' column's position found by MATCH. It looks up the 'Vertex' value from the current row in the 'GroupVertices' table within the 'Vertices' table, dynamically determining the column index. The result is the corresponding value or an error if not found.
