TITLE: Conditional PopOver with popOverEnableOn - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to conditionally enable the popOver feature using the `popOverEnableOn` property. The popOver is only enabled if the specified expression evaluates to true for the current row. In this case, the popOver for the 'id' column is only enabled when `this.id == 1`.
SOURCE: https://github.com/baidu/amis/blob/master/docs/zh-CN/components/popover.md#_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "type": "crud",
    "api": "/api/mock2/sample?waitSeconds=1",
    "columns": [
        {
            "name": "id",
            "label": "ID",
            "popOver": {
                "body": {
                    "type": "tpl",
                    "tpl": "${id}"
                }
            },
            "popOverEnableOn": "this.id == 1"
        },
        {
            "name": "engine",
            "label": "Rendering engine",
            "popOver": {
                "body": {
                    "type": "tpl",
                    "tpl": "${engine}"
                }
            }
        }
    ]
}
```

