TITLE: Function Call Examples in Amis Form
DESCRIPTION: This snippet provides examples of calling various functions within an Amis form using expressions. It showcases functions like IF, MAX, ROUND, AVG, UPPERMONEY, TIMESTAMP, and DATETOSTR with different parameters and data types.
