TITLE: Defining Miscellaneous CSS Classes
DESCRIPTION: This CSS snippet defines various utility classes for controlling visibility, creating lines, removing borders or radius, controlling display properties (block, inline, none), floating elements, clearing floats, applying rounded corners, setting transparent backgrounds, and disabling text selection. It utilizes `@border-color` for the line color.
