TITLE: Configuring Column Events in Amis CRUD
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to configure click, mouseenter, and mouseleave events on columns within an Amis CRUD component.  Each event triggers a toast message displaying the row index and the value of the corresponding column.  The 'onEvent' property within the column definition is used to specify the event listener and associated actions.
